EN: Stealing other people's property is an illegal act.
ZH: 11. 他被指控偷拿了考试答案。
EN: He was accused of stealing the exam answers.
ZH: 12. 警察正在调查一起偷拿案件。
EN: The police are investigating a case of stealing.
