EN: She was suspected of stealing the class fund.
ZH: 14. 公司制定了严格的规章制度来遏制偷拿现象。
EN: The company has established strict regulations to curb stealing.
ZH: 15. 他坚决否认偷拿钱包的指控。
EN: He strongly denied the accusation of stealing the wallet.
ZH: 16. 该员工承认自己偷拿了办公室的耗材。
EN: The employee admitted to stealing office supplies.
ZH: 17. 请你不要再偷拿我的东西了。
EN: Please stop stealing my things.
ZH: 18. 她以偷拿行为受到了学校的处罚。
EN: She was punished by the school for her stealing behavior.
ZH: 19. 政府正在采取强有力的措施打击偷拿犯罪活动。
EN: The government is taking strong measures to combat stealing crimes.
ZH: 20. 这家商店采用了高科技设备以防止顾客偷拿物品。
